hat \"the bad men are coming.\" Nancy and Jonathan show the police what Jonathan caught on camera.','2016-07-15 00:00:00'),(2445,36,2188,8,1,'Chapter Eight: The Upside Down','Dr. Brenner holds Hopper and Joyce for questioning while the boys wait with Eleven in the gym. Back at Will\'s, Nancy and Jonathan prepare for battle.','2016-07-15 00:00:00'),(2446,36,2189,1,2,'Chapter One: MADMAX','As the town preps for Halloween, a high-scoring rival shakes things up at the arcade, and a skeptical Hopper inspects a field of rotting pumpkins.','2017-10-27 00:00:00'),(2447,36,2190,2,2,'Chapter Two: Trick or Treat, Freak','After Will sees something terrible on trick-or-treat night, Mike wonders whether Eleven\'s still out there. Nancy wrestles with the truth about Barb.','2017-10-27 00:00:00'),(2448,36,2191,3,2,'Chapter Three: The Pollywog','Dustin adopts a strange new pet, and Eleven grows increasingly impatient. A well-meaning Bob urges Will to stand up to his fears.','2017-10-27 00:00:00'),(2449,36,2192,4,2,'Chapter Four: Will the Wise','An ailing Will opens up to Joyce -- with disturbing results. While Hopper digs for the truth, Eleven unearths a surprising discovery.','2017-10-27 00:00:00'),(2450,36,2193,5,2,'Chapter Five: Dig Dug','Nancy and Jonathan swap conspiracy theories with a new ally as Eleven searches for someone from her past. “Bob the Brain” tackles a difficult problem.','2017-10-27 00:00:00'),(2451,36,2194,6,2,'Chapter Six: The Spy','Will\'s connection to a shadowy evil grows stronger, but no one\'s quite sure how to stop it. Elsewhere, Dustin and Steve forge an unlikely bond.','2017-10-27 00:00:00'),(2452,36,2195,7,2,'Chapter Seven: The Lost Sister','Psychic visions draw Eleven to a band of violent outcasts and an angry girl with a shadowy past.','2017-10-27 00:00:00'),(2453,36,2196,8,2,'Chapter Eight: The Mind Flayer','An unlikely hero steps forward when a deadly development puts the Hawkins Lab on lockdown, trapping Will and several others inside.','2017-10-2