-11-28 00:00:00'),(2567,38,2270,13,2,'Critical Mass','When an operative of the Trust plants a bomb in Atlantis, the team must find a spy within their own ranks before the Wraith arrive and discover the city.','2005-12-05 00:00:00'),(2568,38,2271,14,2,'Grace Under Pressure','When Dr. McKay is trapped underwater in a sinking Puddle Jumper, his only chance for survival may be an hallucination of Samantha Carter.','2005-12-10 00:00:00'),(2569,38,2272,15,2,'The Tower','The team finds a world that possesses Ancient defense technology, where Colonel Sheppard finds himself a pawn in the rivalry between the heirs to the throne.','2005-12-19 00:00:00'),(2570,38,2273,16,2,'The Long Goodbye','The team discovers two pods that contain the minds of alien beings, who take control of Weir and Sheppard\'s bodies to continue their personal war.','2006-01-02 00:00:00'),(2571,38,2274,17,2,'Coup D\'etat','After a team from Atlantis goes missing, the expedition finds itself in the middle of a Genii coup.','2006-01-09 00:00:00'),(2572,38,2275,18,2,'Michael','An amnesiac young Lieutenant in Atlantis suffers from disturbing nightmares that he is a Wraith, only to make a shocking discovery about himself.','2006-01-16 00:00:00'),(2573,38,2276,19,2,'Inferno','Sheppard\'s team meets a civilization about to be destroyed by a super-volcano, and is trapped there when the Stargate is destroyed during the evacuation.','2006-01-23 00:00:00'),(2574,38,2277,20,2,'Allies (1)','Michael and his Wraith faction arrive at Atlantis to propose an alliance, hoping to use the retrovirus to transform their Wraith enemies into prey.','2006-01-30 00:00:00'),(2575,38,2278,1,3,'No Man\'s Land (2)','The team desperately attempts to stop two Wraith hive ships from reaching Earth. Sheppard must rely on an old foe to rescue McKay and Ronon.','2006-07-14 00:00:00'),(2576,38,2279,2,3,'Misbegotten (3)','The Atlantis team must decide the fate of a colony of Wraith they have turned into humans. Dr. Weir must defend her leadership when she is evaluated by the I.O.A.','2006-07-21 00:00:00'),(2577,38,2280,3,3,'Irresistible','Sheppard\'s team meets an obnoxious man who is adored by all thanks to a secret that he carries -- and who has an unexpected affect on them.','2006-07-28 00:00:00'),(2578,38,2281,4,3,'Sateda','Ronon Dex is captured by the Wraith and returned to his homeworld, where he is haunted by his past as he is forced to once again become their prey.','2006-08-04 00:00:00'),(2579,38,2282,5,3,'Progeny','Weir and the team visit an advanced civilization that split off from the Lanteans thousands of years ago, but discover that they may not have left Atlantis in peace.','2006-08-11 00:00:00'),(2580,38,2283,6,3,'The Real World','Elizabeth Weir wakes up in a mental institution, where she is told that the expedition to Atlantis and the Stargate are figments of her imagination.','2006-08-18 00:00:00'),(2581,38,2284,7,3,'Common Ground','Colonel Sheppard finds himself the prisoner of a Genii commander, along with a desperately hungry Wraith who has been separated from his hive.','2006-08-25 00:00:00'),(2582,38,2285,8,3,'McKay and Mrs. Miller','Rodney McKay is reunited with his estranged sister back on Earth, who has given up a brilliant career as a scientist to raise a family.','2006-09-08 00:00:00'),(2583,38,2286,9,3,'Phantoms','Sheppard and Ronon are influenced by a mind-altering device created by the Wraith while on a mission to rescue a lost team.','2006-09-15 00:00:00'),(2584,38,2287,10,3,'The Return (1)','The Atlantis expedition is stunned to learn that a ship full of Ancients is returning to reclaim their lost city.','2006-09-22 00:00:00'),(2585,38,2288,11,3,'The Return (2)','The Atlantis team goes against orders to try and save Atlantis from Replicator control -- and to rescue General O\'Neill and Richard Woolsey, who are trapped in the occupied city.','2006-11-20 00:00:00'),(2586,38,2289,12,3,'Echoes','The inhabitants of Atlantis begin to suffer ill effects when the planet\'s whale 